<subSubSection lastPageId="2" lastPageNumber="538" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1052,2016]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">
Forty-five years after the introduction of 
<taxonomicName authority=", Kraatz (1882)" authorityName=", Kraatz" authorityYear="1882" box="[658,926,1593,1619]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[658,757,1593,1619]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">Haplidia</emphasis>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Kraatz, G." box="[770,926,1593,1619]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="33 - 42" refId="ref7415" refString="Kraatz, G. (1882) Revision der europaisch-syrischen Arten der Melolonthiden-Gattung Haplidia Hope. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift, 26, 33 - 42. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnd. 48018820202" type="journal article" year="1882">Kraatz (1882)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
published the first comprehensive revision of the genus. Regarding 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1855" box="[394,551,1629,1655]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fissa">
<emphasis box="[394,551,1629,1655]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">Haplidia fissa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, he identified as such some female specimens from 
<collectingCountry box="[1133,1230,1629,1655]" name="Lebanon" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">Lebanon</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[1244,1351,1629,1656]" country="Lebanon" name="Beyrouth" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">Beyrouth</collectingRegion>
) that in his opinion best agreed with the description of the Syrian—Mesopotamian female of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1855" box="[1084,1167,1665,1691]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fissa">
<emphasis box="[1084,1167,1665,1691]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">H. fissa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and used the associated male specimens for a supplemental description of the species, thus providing the basis for the misidentifications that followed. Subsequent authors of descriptive and faunistic articles, revisions and catalogues followed 
<bibRefCitation author="Kraatz, G." box="[1264,1436,1737,1763]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="33 - 42" refId="ref7415" refString="Kraatz, G. (1882) Revision der europaisch-syrischen Arten der Melolonthiden-Gattung Haplidia Hope. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift, 26, 33 - 42. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnd. 48018820202" type="journal article" year="1882">Kraatz’s (1882)</bibRefCitation>
interpretation (
<emphasis box="[317,357,1774,1799]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">e.g.</emphasis>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Reitter, E." box="[371,512,1773,1799]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="93 - 303" refId="ref7798" refString="Reitter, E. (1902) Bestimmungs-Tabelle der Melolonthidae aus der europaischen fauna und angrenzenden landern, enthaltend die gruppen der Pachydemini, Sericini und Melolonthini. Verhandlungen des Naturforschenden Vereines in Brunn, 40, 93 - 303. [1901]" type="journal article" year="1902">Reitter 1902</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Dalla Torre, K. W. von" box="[523,715,1773,1799]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="135 - 290" refId="ref6945" refString="Dalla Torre, K. W. von. (1912) Pars 49. Scarabaeidae: Melolonthidae III. In: Junk W. &amp; Schenkling S. (Eds): Coleopterorum Catalogus. Vol. XX. W. Junk, Berlin, pp. 135 - 290." type="book chapter" year="1912">Dalla Torre 1912</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Petrovitz, R." box="[726,891,1773,1799]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="325 - 343" refId="ref7692" refString="Petrovitz, R. (1967) Ergebnisse zoologischer sammelreisen in der Turkei. Annalen des Naturhistorischen Museums in Wien, 70, 325 - 343." type="journal article" year="1967">Petrovitz 1967</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Petrovitz, R." box="[902,960,1773,1799]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="38 - 45" refId="ref7719" refString="Petrovitz, R. (1970) Scarabaeidae aus Iran. Entomologie et Phytopathologie Appliquees, 29, 38 - 45." type="journal article" year="1970">1970</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Petrovitz, R." box="[972,1042,1773,1799]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="215 - 238" refId="ref7741" refString="Petrovitz, R. (1971 a) Scarabaeidae from the Near East. Israel Journal of Entomology, 6, 215 - 238." type="journal article" year="1971">1971a</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Baraud, J." box="[1054,1200,1772,1799]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="191 - 196" refId="ref6465" refString="Baraud, J. (1975) Descriptions de cinq nouvelles especes palearctiques de Coleopteres Scarabaeoidea. Nouvelle Revue d'Entomologie, 5, 191 - 196." type="journal article" year="1975">Baraud 1975</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Montreuil, O." box="[1211,1389,1772,1799]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="129 - 131" refId="ref7581" refString="Montreuil, O. (2005) Contribution a l'etude du genre Haplidia Hope: description de deux nouvelles especes du Liban (Coleoptera, Melolonthinae). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 110 (2), 129 - 131." type="journal article" year="2005">Montreuil 2005</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1052,2016]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">
Also 
<bibRefCitation author="Baraud, J." box="[262,445,1809,1835]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="539 - 580" refId="ref6524" refString="Baraud, J. (1988) Contribution a l'etude du genre Haplidia Hope (Coleoptera Scarabaeoidea Melolonthidae). Revue Suisse de Zoologie, 95, 539 - 580. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 79672" type="journal article" year="1988">Baraud’s (1988)</bibRefCitation>
revision of the whole genus maintained the identification of the species sensu 
<bibRefCitation author="Kraatz, G." pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="33 - 42" refId="ref7415" refString="Kraatz, G. (1882) Revision der europaisch-syrischen Arten der Melolonthiden-Gattung Haplidia Hope. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift, 26, 33 - 42. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnd. 48018820202" type="journal article" year="1882">Kraatz (1882)</bibRefCitation>
. This revision included the study of the Kraatz and Petrovitz collections and the redescription of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1855" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fissa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">Haplidia fissa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
male (sensu Kraatz), but not an examination of the 
<typeStatus box="[790,838,1881,1907]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">type</typeStatus>
in Burmeister’s collection. Kraatz’s concept of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1855" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fissa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="537">Haplidia fissa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was therefore reconfirmed and, as such, accepted also by 
<bibRefCitation author="Sabatinelli, G." box="[946,1153,1917,1943]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="5 - 50" refId="ref7842" refString="Sabatinelli, G. (1991) Note sul genere Haplidia Burm. con descizione di H. baraudi n. sp. Bollettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 123, 4 5 - 50." type="journal article" year="1991">Sabatinelli (1991)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Chikatunov, V. &amp; Pavlicek, T." pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="37 - 65" refId="ref6815" refString="Chikatunov, V. &amp; Pavlicek, T. (1997) Catalogue of the beetles (Coleoptera) in Israel and adjacent areas: 1. Scarabaeoidea. Klapalekiana, 33, 37 - 65." type="journal article" year="1997">Chikatunov &amp; Pavlíček (1997)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Keith, D." box="[239,389,1953,1979]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="380 - 387" refId="ref7237" refString="Keith, D. (2000 a) Contribution a la connaissance des Scarabaeoidea du Moyen Orient: taxons nouveaux ou peu connus (Coleoptera). Lambillionea, 100, 380 - 387." type="journal article" year="2000">Keith (2000a</bibRefCitation>
, b), 
<bibRefCitation author="Keith, D. &amp; Lo Cascio, P." box="[436,731,1952,1979]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="139 - 142" refId="ref7375" refString="Keith, D. &amp; Lo Cascio, P. (2005) A new Haplidia Hope from Nisyros Island (Dodecanese, Greece) with a catalogue of the genus. Lambillionea, 105, 139 - 142." type="journal article" year="2005">Keith &amp; Lo Cascio (2005)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Montreuil, O." box="[742,937,1952,1979]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="129 - 131" refId="ref7581" refString="Montreuil, O. (2005) Contribution a l'etude du genre Haplidia Hope: description de deux nouvelles especes du Liban (Coleoptera, Melolonthinae). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 110 (2), 129 - 131." type="journal article" year="2005">Montreuil (2005)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Smetana, A. &amp; Kral, D." box="[949,1213,1953,1980]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="207 - 228" refId="ref7942" refString="Smetana, A. &amp; Kral, D. (2006) Rhizotrogini. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Smetana, A. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera, Volume 3. Scarabaeoidea-Scirtoidea-Dascilloidea-Buprestoidea-Byrrhoidea. Apollo Books, Stenstrup, pp. 207 - 228." type="book chapter" year="2006">Smetana &amp; Král (2006)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Bezdek, A." box="[1224,1390,1953,1980]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="249 - 280" refId="ref6643" refString="Bezdek, A. (2016) Rhizotrogini. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Volume 3. Scarabaeoidea, Scirtoidea, Dascilloidea, Buprestoidea, Byrrhoidea. Revised and updated edition. Brill, Leiden, Boston, pp. 249 - 280." type="book chapter" year="2016">Bezděk (2016)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Miessen, G." box="[151,329,1989,2016]" pageId="1" pageNumber="537" pagination="57 - 73" refId="ref7539" refString="Miessen, G. (2016) Essais sur le genre Aplidia Hope 1837 a Chypre et commentaires sur quelques especes limitrophes (Coleoptera, Scarabaeoidea, Melolonthidae, Rhizotrogini). Entomologie Faunistique-Faunistic Entomology, 69, 57 - 73." type="journal article" year="2016">Miessen (2016)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,153,431]" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">
After examination of the female 
<typeStatus box="[562,610,153,179]" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1855" box="[647,804,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="538" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fissa">
<emphasis box="[647,804,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">Haplidia fissa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
that we could locate in Burmeister’s collection we could ascertain (Sehnal, in press) that it belongs to the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Keith, 2001" authorityName="Keith" authorityYear="2001" box="[771,1061,189,215]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Medeotrogus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="538" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[771,918,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">Medeotrogus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Keith, D." box="[925,1061,189,215]" pageId="2" pageNumber="538" pagination="75 - 78" refId="ref7308" refString="Keith, D. (2001) Contribution a la connaissance des Scarabaeoidea du Proche et du Moyen-Orient (9 e note). Description de Medeotrogus linnavuorii n. gen., n. sp. d'Irak et d'Iran (Col. Melolonthidae) et d' Adoretus kashmarensis, n. sp. d'Iran. Symbioses, Nouvelle Serie, 5, 75 - 78." type="journal article" year="2001">Keith, 2001</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, recently described on specimens from 
<collectingCountry box="[212,257,225,251]" name="Iraq" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">Iraq</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[311,360,225,251]" name="Iran" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">Iran</collectingCountry>
. Among characters of the genus are some that are similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName=", Kraatz" authorityYear="1882" box="[1033,1133,225,251]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="538" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1033,1133,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">Haplidia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, such as emarginated clypeus, integuments ranging from glossy to matte chestnut brown, the male body symmetrically elongate, whereas in females the posterior part of the elytra is markedly wider. Such similarity, and the lack of study of the primary 
<typeStatus box="[1381,1432,297,323]" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">type</typeStatus>
, caused the misinterpretation of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Burmeister" authorityYear="1855" box="[504,662,333,359]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="538" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fissa">
<emphasis box="[504,662,333,359]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">Haplidia fissa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,153,431]" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">
As no name is available for 
<taxonomicName authority="sensu Kraatz (1882)" authorityName="sensu Kraatz" authorityYear="1882" box="[513,905,369,395]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="538" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fissa">
<emphasis box="[513,671,369,395]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">Haplidia fissa</emphasis>
sensu 
<bibRefCitation author="Kraatz, G." box="[747,905,369,395]" pageId="2" pageNumber="538" pagination="33 - 42" refId="ref7415" refString="Kraatz, G. (1882) Revision der europaisch-syrischen Arten der Melolonthiden-Gattung Haplidia Hope. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift, 26, 33 - 42. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnd. 48018820202" type="journal article" year="1882">Kraatz (1882)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, we propose for the species commonly referred as such the new name 
<taxonomicName authority="Sehnal, Montreuil &amp; Uliana" authorityName="Sehnal, Montreuil &amp; Uliana" authorityYear="2020" box="[402,1038,405,431]" class="Insecta" family="Melolonthidae" genus="Haplidia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="538" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="karlaeschneiderae" status="new species">
<emphasis box="[402,716,405,431]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="538">Haplidia karlaeschneiderae</emphasis>
Sehnal, Montreuil &amp; Uliana
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1049,1184,405,431]" pageId="2" pageNumber="538" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
.
</paragraph>
